<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h4><center> Your resignation request has been approved </center></h4>

<p> This is to inform that the resignation request created by <%= @employee.try(:prefix) %> <%= @employee.try(:first_name) %>  <%= @employee.try(:middle_name) %> <%= @employee.try(:last_name) %> on <%= @employee_resignation.try(:resignation_date) %>, has been approved by the HR Head. </p>

<p> For further details, kindly contact your reporting manager or HR Team. </p>

<h4>Details of the Resignation:-</h4>

<p> Employee ID:- <%= @employee.try(:manual_employee_code) %> </p>

<p> Employee Name:- <%= @employee.try(:prefix) %> <%= @employee.try(:first_name) %>  <%= @employee.try(:middle_name) %> <%= @employee.try(:last_name) %> </p>

<p> Reason of Separation:- <%= @employee_resignation.try(:reason) %> </p>

<p>Best Regards,</p>

<p> HR Team </p>
  </body>
</html>

